To compile go to './firmware' directory and type 'make'. It create main.hex file to burn flash in ATtiny2313 used in adapter.
You should also set bitfuses CKSEL0..3, CKDIV, CKOUT  to '1' eg using external oscillator, no divider.
For compile you have to install avr-gcc.

Script usb_rules_install adds USB of adapter to group 'lp', so to run program you do not need to be root.

